<br>
The clerics in my guild love having druids in their group on raids. I never wait long after joining the raid before getting an invite. (sometimes they fight over me lol) The fact is, between RG and backup healing and topping off, druids save their clerics a ton of mana, which speeds up the raid (or group) with more pulls. <br>
<br>
